<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%-user.username.toLowerCase()%>'s Studio</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM" crossorigin="anonymous">
  
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
</head>
  <body>
      <header class="p-3 text-bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
            <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2 mb-lg-0 text-white text-decoration-none">
              <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32" role="img" aria-label="Bootstrap"><use xlink:href="#bootstrap"></use></svg>
            </a>
    
            <ul class="nav col-12 col-lg-auto me-lg-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0">
              <li><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">Studio</a></li>
              <% if(user){ %>
                <li><a href="/balance" class="nav-link px-2 text-secondary">Balance</a></li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
    
            <form class="col-12 col-lg-auto mb-3 mb-lg-0 me-lg-3" role="search">
              <input type="search" class="form-control form-control-dark text-bg-dark" placeholder="Search..." aria-label="Search">
            </form>
    
            <div class="text-end">
              <% if(user){ %>
                <p class="mb-0 text-body-secondary"><%-user.wallet %> BTC</p>
              <% } else{ %>  
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2">Login</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning">Sign-up</button>
             <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
    <main class="container">
        <div class="row g-5">
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <h3 class="pb-4 mb-4 fst-italic border-bottom">
                CoinX Trading Platform
              </h3>
        
              <article class="blog-post">
                <h2 class="display-5 link-body-emphasis mb-1">Deposit Bitcoin</h2>
                <p class="blog-post-meta"><a href="#">Generate Deposit QR Code</a></p>
                <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                    Attention! Multiple deposits to the same Bitcoin address will not be accredited by our system.
                </div>
                <p>Enhance Your Deposits: Embrace the Future with Ethereum's Swift Network â€“ Coming Soon!</p>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#createNewDeposit" aria-controls="createNewDeposit">
                    Create Deposit
                  </button>
                  
                  <div class="offcanvas offcanvas-start" tabindex="-1" id="createNewDeposit" aria-labelledby="createNewDepositLabel">
                    <div class="offcanvas-header">
                      <h5 class="offcanvas-title" id="createNewDepositLabel">Deposit Form</h5>
                      <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offcanvas-body">
                        <label for="username" class="form-label">Amount to deposit</label>
                        <form>
                        <div class="input-group has-validation">
                          <span class="input-group-text">$</span>
                          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="depositAmount" placeholder="0.00" required="">
                          <small class="mt-3 w-100" id="convertedCurrency"></small>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                        <button type="button" id="generateQrCode" class="mt-3 btn btn-secondary">Generate QR Code</button>
                        <div id="generatedQrCode"></div>
                        <div id="depositAlert"></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                <hr>
                <p>Please allow time for your Bitcoin deposit to confirm on the blockchain.</p>
               
            </article>
        
                  <article class="blog-post">
                    <h2 class="display-5 link-body-emphasis mb-1">Request Account Payout</h2>
                    <p class="blog-post-meta">Last account transaction made January 1, 2021 <a href="#">Download account statement</a></p>
            
                    <p>To ensure smooth and successful payouts, it is essential to have a valid Bitcoin wallet linked to your account. By providing a valid wallet address, you can securely receive your earnings and rewards in Bitcoin directly. Additionally, please note that payouts are only valid to an account balance that meets or exceeds a minimum of $10 BTC equivalent. This balance threshold helps us streamline our payment process and ensures that our members receive substantial payouts</p>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Request Payout</button>
                    <hr>
                    <p>For our valued registered members, we strive to offer a smooth and timely payout process. Payouts are typically processed within 1-3 business days, ensuring you receive your funds promptly. We value your trust and are committed to providing hassle-free transactions for all your earnings and rewards. Thank you for being a part of our community, and if you have any questions regarding your payouts, feel free to reach out to our support team for assistance.</p>
                      </article>
            
            </div>
        
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="position-sticky" style="top: 2rem;">
                
                <div class="p-4">
                  <h4 class="fst-italic">Subscribe to Social Media</h4>
                  <ol class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Telegram</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Discord</a></li>
                  </ol>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
    </main>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/coinx.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      $(function () {
        
      })
    </script>
</body>
</html>